<p><span class="anchor" id="p28"></span>١٩٤٤ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الْحسن:</span> روح بن عبد الْمُؤمن<a href="#p28" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
